.blockchain
  .container(data-aos="fade-right")
    h2 Blockchain
    .wrap-chart.clearfix
      .chart
        img(src="images/charts/blockchain/chart.png", data-rjs="images/charts/blockchain/chart@2x.png", alt="")
      ul.list.list--1
        li.item.item--1
          .item__icn 1
          .item__text ERC - 721 token used to store the lineage of each piece of art
        li.item.item--2
          .item__icn.item__icn--style-2 2
          .item__text The metadata of the token keeps a hash of the current owner and transaction history
        li.item.item--3
          .item__icn 3
          .item__text With every trade, we take the latest block number, owner details and sale info along-side a UUID and hash everything again
      ul.list.list--2  
        li.item.item--4
          .item__icn.item__icn--style-2 4
          .item__text The history of movement of the art on the ArtPro system is stored in the immutable blockchain
        li.item.item--5
          .item__icn 5
          .item__text The authenticity of each transaction can be proven by cross-referencing with the corresponding ethereum block

